title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Jan 13 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Jan 13 2022
description:
Fauci says everyone will get Omicron, Clay tests positive yesterday and says he's almost back to "100 percent" now. Buck's reaction: "My man Clay being a hero today. We’re here, we’re a duo, we’re a team, a tag team. We’re gonna get it done." Biden's nonsensical rambling covid speech -- and this, Clay emphasizes, when he's reading right off a teleprompter. C&B applaud Ted Cruz ripping media on mask questions and the sound of his banging on the podium. Confused Biden and Harris double down on failed covid strategy. Sinema sinks Biden bid to kill the filibuster. RNC threatens pullout from presidential debates.
